name: Eternal darkness
description: This photo was taken when I was suffering from depression. I came to a point where I couldn't take it anymore and went out for a drive, and found a train track that leads to a tunnel. I wasn't sure if there's gonna be train incoming but I went in there and took the shot. Format : JPEG / Size : 3,376 x 4,501 / Shot, edited by Cloudy Night.
